<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8">
        <title>{% block title %}Bienvenue !{% endblock %}</title>
        <link rel="icon" href="data:image/svg+xml,<svg xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22 viewBox=%220 0 128 128%22><text y=%221.2em%22 font-size=%2296%22>⚫️</text></svg>">
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/bootswatch/5.3.1/lux/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha512-AEz+khxSceaCAGjFlMVVP44z6/Wn0VAE2Q5aSpQR7tHORYsYP2vzU7W3OSvncmYZOX82xCJYd4bq/0iR+Qp9fw==" crossorigin="anonymous" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" />
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.10.5/font/bootstrap-icons.css">
        {% block stylesheets %}
        {% endblock %}

        {% block javascripts %}
        {% endblock %}
    </head>
    <body>
    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg bg-body-tertiary" data-bs-theme="dark">
  <div class="container-fluid">
    <a class="navbar-brand" href="{{ path('home') }}">Hotel House</a>
    <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#navbarColor04" aria-controls="navbarColor04" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
      <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
    </button>
    <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarColor04">
      <ul class="navbar-nav me-auto">
        <li class="nav-item">
          <a class="nav-link active" href="{{ path('home') }}">Accueil
            <span class="visually-hidden">(current)</span>
          </a>
        </li>
        <li class="nav-item">
          <a class="nav-link" href="{{ path('app_chambre') }}">Chambre</a>
        </li>
        <li class="nav-item">
          <a class="nav-link" href="{{ path('app_restaurant') }}">Restaurant</a>
        </li>
        <li class="nav-item">
          <a class="nav-link" href="{{ path('app_spa') }}">Spa</a>
        </li>
        <li class="nav-item">
          <a class="nav-link" href="{{ path('app_avis') }}">Avis</a>
        </li>
        <li class="nav-item dropdown">
          <a class="nav-link dropdown-toggle" data-bs-toggle="dropdown" href="" role="button" aria-haspopup="true" aria-expanded="false">l'hôtel</a>
          <div class="dropdown-menu">
            <a class="dropdown-item" href="{{ path('app_information') }}">Qui sommes-nous?</a>
            <a class="dropdown-item" href="{{ path('app_acces') }}">Accès</a>
            <a class="dropdown-item" href="{{ path('app_contact') }}">Contact</a>
        </li>
        <li class="nav-item">
          <a class="nav-link" href="">Actualités</a>
        </li>
        <li class="nav-item">
          <a class="nav-link" href="{{ path('app_contact') }}">Contact</a>
        </li>
        {% if is_granted("ROLE_USER") %}
        
        <li class="nav-item">
          <a class="nav-link" href="{{ path('admin') }}">BackOffice</a>
        </li>
        {% endif %}

      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</nav>

        {% block body %}{% endblock %}
        {# ! Footer  #}
<footer class="text-center text-lg-start bg-body-tertiary text-muted p-4" data-bs-theme="dark">


  <section class="text-white">
    <div class="container text-center text-md-start mt-5">
      <div class="row mt-3">
        <div class="col-md-3 col-lg-4 col-xl-3 mx-auto mb-4">
          <h6 class="text-uppercase fw-bold mb-4 text-white-50">
            <i class="fas fa-gem me-3"></i>Hotel House
          </h6>
          <p>
            Découvrez l'élégance, le confort et l'hospitalité authentique dans notre oasis de tranquillité. Bienvenue à Hotel House, votre chez-vous loin de chez vous.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="col-md-2 col-lg-2 col-xl-2 mx-auto mb-4">
          <h6 class="text-uppercase fw-bold mb-4 text-white-50">
            Réseaux
          </h6>
          <p>
            <a href="#!" class="text-white text-decoration-none"><i class="bi bi-twitter"></i> @hotelhouse</a>
          </p>
          <p>
            <a href="#!" class="text-white text-decoration-none"><i class="bi bi-facebook"></i> Hotel House</a>
          </p>
          <p>
            <a href="#!" class="text-white text-decoration-none"><i class="bi bi-instagram"></i> @hotelhouse</a>
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="col-md-3 col-lg-2 col-xl-2 mx-auto mb-4">
          <h6 class="text-uppercase fw-bold mb-4 text-white-50">
            Liens divers
          </h6>
          <p>
            <a href="{{ path('app_mentionlegales') }}" class="text-reset">Mentions Légales</a>
          </p>
          <p>
            <a href="#!" class="text-reset">Conditions Générales de Vente</a>
          </p>
          <p>
            <a href="#!" class="text-reset">Plan du Site</a>
          </p>
          <p>
            <a href="#!" class="text-reset">Imprimer la page</a>
          </p>
          <p>
            <a href="#!" class="text-reset">S'inscrire à la newsletter</a>
          </p>
          <p>
            <a href="#!" class="text-reset">Partage</a>
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="col-md-4 col-lg-3 col-xl-3 mx-auto mb-md-0 mb-4">
          <h6 class="text-uppercase fw-bold mb-4 text-white-50">Contact</h6>
          <p><i class="bi bi-geo-alt-fill"></i> New York, NY 10012, US</p>
          <p>
            <i class="bi bi-envelope-at-fill"></i>
            hotelhouse@gmail.com
          </p>
          <p><i class="bi bi-telephone-fill"></i> + 01 234 567 88</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</footer>
{#!  Footer  #}
        <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.1/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-HwwvtgBNo3bZJJLYd8oVXjrBZt8cqVSpeBNS5n7C8IVInixGAoxmnlMuBnhbgrkm" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    </body>
</html>
